        "url": "en/about/human/",
        "content": "Human Tribe \u00b6 This team is where all the guilds and squads related to the human orientation of the project are developed. This element ensures that whatever we do is focused on the context in which our users live. Due to our efforts to reach people in places without access to stable currency, our users live in countries enduring difficult situations . Usually, there is little (if any) technological development and people live with stress and mistrust. Our team has to operate not only understanding these realities, but truly empathizing with the people who live there, in order for our product to be really useful to them. Our vision is creating a simpler and more human user experience. Those who make up this tribe must have passion for social impact , regardless of the area in which they operate. This is arguably the heart of our project",
