        "url": "en/app/coverage/",
        "content": "Access to Essential Global Financial Services \u00b6 We believe in a future where anybody in the world can access essential financial services, no matter where on the planet they find themselves. We\u2019re developing the infrastructure that will make this future a reality. We have a two stage strategy that lets us open access and progressively integrate countries into the app. This way we can open our doors to more places and gradually roll out local solutions. You can track our progress through the stages here: Current worldwide coverage \u00b6 Legend \u00b6 Stage 1: Crypto Stage 2: Local currency integration Stage 1: Crypto The first stage lets users make transactions in cryptocurrency. Users in countries in this stage have access to an account in stable currency (RSV), and can deposit and withdraw with other stablecoins, bitcoin, and ether. They can also send money in local currency to countries that are already in the second stage, such as Argentina, Colombia, Panama, Peru and Venezuela. Stage 2: Local currency integration This stage integrates fiat currency into the app. Users will have the option to make deposits and withdrawals to and from local financial institutions in their countries. This process aims to open access to more and more countries until complete coverage is offered to the Americas. Once we reach this goal, we will turn our attention to offering app access in other regions of the world. We are a human project with a dream to make economic connections possible between all people. This dream will take time to achieve, but our vision is oriented to the long-term.",
        "title": "Current Worldwide Coverage"
